{
  "texts": [
    "The LLM training process usually takes weeks or months and requires computing resources such as efficient GPUs and sufficient memory.",
    "Language interpretation [69], chatbots [70], summarization [71], and cognitive reasoning [72] represent a group of many applications to which LLM can contribute.",
    "Moreover, this technology is also used to improve and speed up various language-related activities in fields such as banking [73], healthcare [74], and education [67].",
    "LLM has many advantages, including the ability to perform NLP-related tasks without special training.",
    "It can be attributed to the experimental results because there are no clear instructions for performing specific tasks."
  ]
}